isTextContent

public static boolean isTextContent(java.lang.String contentType)
Indicates whether the content type is text or not. The following content types are considered as text: - any type starting with 'text/' - any type starting with 'application/' and followed by 'xml', for example: 'application/atom+xml' - application/ecmascript - application/json - application/javascript - message/http

Returns:
Returns true if the content type is text otherwise return false;
